des:
Popotan Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your Popotan products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Popotan" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Popotan account in our " Popotan" app;
(3). You need to have some Popotan devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Popotan" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Popotan Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Popotan Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Popotan Smart", and you'll be navigated to Popotan login page;
(9). Input your Popotan account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
